s eligible to representTeam GBbut opted to play for Ireland three years ago.\", \"from\": 213, \"to\": 332, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 233, \"end\": 249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9045682569487787, \"rank\": 0.1054997699885964, \"text\": \"Northern Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 308, \"end\": 315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8531401683544441, \"rank\": 0.1688035168115915, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics  In Tokyo, McIlroy and his teammate Shane Lowry finished just outside the medals as they placed fourth but the pair are now aiming for a podium spot in Paris.\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 410, \"end\": 415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.998843363245579, \"rank\": 0.001157187545960065, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 442, \"end\": 453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Lowry_(golfer)\", \"score\": 0.9805012734846731, \"rank\": 0.019886363636360344, \"text\": \"Shane Lowry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Lowry_(golfer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Lowry_(golfer)\"}, {\"begin\": 558, \"end\": 563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997116902, \"rank\": 2.8840039655604994e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McIlroy has revealed that his decision to represent Ireland and not Team GB at the Olympics is because of the decision he made during his amateur career.\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 618, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8531401683544441, \"rank\": 0.1688035168115915, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 634, \"end\": 641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9648234188310846, \"rank\": 0.03645908717652252, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before turning professional, McIlroy played for Ireland and the four-time major winner says he had no reason to change for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 769, \"end\": 776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8531401683544441, \"rank\": 0.1688035168115915, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an agreement between the Olympic Federation of Ireland and the British Olympic Association, athletes are permitted to choose which team they wish to represent.\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 1021, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 925, \"end\": 952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking in an interview withThe Guardianearlier this month, McIlroy explained why he decided to represent Ireland.\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1130, \"end\": 1137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8531401683544441, \"rank\": 0.1688035168115915, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I had a sense of resentment towards the Olympics because I had always tried to stay so neutral and it presented me with this option of; what are you going to do?'\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1303, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"McIlroy said.\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1317, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I had to get over that.\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All of my amateur career I played for Ireland.\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1390, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1382, \"end\": 1389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8531401683544441, \"rank\": 0.1688035168115915, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was very proud to play for Ireland.\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1420, \"end\": 1427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8531401683544441, \"rank\": 0.1688035168115915, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So why would I do anything differently as a professional?\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1486, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Tokyo felt like a throwback to the amateur days.\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1489, \"end\": 1494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.998843363245579, \"rank\": 0.001157187545960065, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All the federations were there.\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1569, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Seeing people from the amateur game who I had not seen for decades.\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1637, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I really enjoyed the experience and I am sure Paris will be even better because I will get to go to some of the other events.\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1763, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1684, \"end\": 1689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997116902, \"rank\": 2.8840039655604994e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's a bit like the Ryder Cup, I made comments before I had experienced it.\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am excited to go back.'\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1867, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking more about his decision in 2021, McIlroy said: 'I made it more difficult for myself than I needed to.\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1979, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'My feeling towards it was more 'What will other people think?'\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 2044, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Once I got that out of my head and just tried to do what was right for me, then it became easy.\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was me wrestling with all of those things.\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2186, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'As I said, previously, once I left trying not to upset anyone aside, then it was actually a pretty easy decision.\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2302, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The decision was I am going to play golf for the country or the nation that I have always played for through my junior and amateur days and now into the professional game.\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2474, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Even though the Olympics has given me this choice, there really wasn't a choice because all I have done throughout my life is play golf for Ireland so why would that change just because the tournament has changed.\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2690, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2617, \"end\": 2624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8531401683544441, \"rank\": 0.1688035168115915, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was my decision.'\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2715, \"to\": 2763, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:What time is Andy Murray's Olympic doubles quarter-final today?\", \"from\": 2837, \"to\": 2910, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Olympic triathlete makes disgusting revelation after swimming in polluted Paris river  ArrowMORE:Olympic gold medallist awkwardly squirms in confrontation over Strictly 2024 'leak'  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2912, \"to\": 3214, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2996, \"end\": 3001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997116902, \"rank\": 2.8840039655604994e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 3216, \"to\": 3347, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 3348, \"to\": 3520, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3410, \"end\": 3416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\", \"score\": 0.6784377202962604, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Punchy\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 3522, \"to\": 3653, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 3654, \"to\": 3714